{"tid":445581,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(求教)想由丹東去北韓","createTime":"2017-10-23T13:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T06:52:05.000Z","uid":51200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"74f680a83c74c7e5c054200f65bafa7ad14e3684","tid":445581,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"話說小弟今年年尾可能去哈爾濱看冰雕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想從吉林去丹東去北韓<br />\n之前係高登睇過有啲可以信賴嘅當地旅行社<br />\n仲有連登有個po寫北韓遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係個po唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網Google發現d丹東當地旅行社網站好流，<br />\n價錢差幾遠，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又聽過話香港人跟團會貴過大陸人跟團 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲打可以推介下丹東當地嘅旅行團/社，<br />\n同講下價錢比小弟參考一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想join大概係4日3夜，住羊角酒店，<br />\n打個卡嗰類團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a8f8c453676ebf8fdee1e76f9439654daaf26a","tid":445581,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:38:50.000Z","msg":"而家去都幾危險"},{"pid":"0971b23f9d050c7ed1b9e40442833475dae66181","tid":445581,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家去都幾危險</blockquote><br />\n爛命一條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1d516d375269630542002c58b15269d3d6b126","tid":445581,"uid":120488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:10:28.000Z","msg":"其實間間旅行社都冇方別，價錢唔同只是住的酒店唔同<br />\n去到朝鮮都是統一路線，由朝鮮領隊帶隊<br />\n香港人是會比大陸人貴500<br />\n記得提前10日預先比定護照資料同相旅行社申請朝鮮簽證（相掃描都得）"},{"pid":"3cb85dc85c6de52609028f0c929cf572f7085be1","tid":445581,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:38:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實間間旅行社都冇方別，價錢唔同只是住的酒店唔同<br />\n去到朝鮮都是統一路線，由朝鮮領隊帶隊<br />\n香港人是會比大陸人貴500<br />\n記得提前10日預先比定護照資料同相旅行社申請朝鮮簽證（相掃描都得）</blockquote><br />\n洗唔洗係香港簽定證先？定可以直接比旅行社班人搞？"},{"pid":"1297604fe669b76bfb8427b0b10d23e8daeed8f6","tid":445581,"uid":120488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實間間旅行社都冇方別，價錢唔同只是住的酒店唔同<br />\n去到朝鮮都是統一路線，由朝鮮領隊帶隊<br />\n香港人是會比大陸人貴500<br />\n記得提前10日預先比定護照資料同相旅行社申請朝鮮簽證（相掃描都得）</blockquote><br />\n洗唔洗係香港簽定證先？定可以直接比旅行社班人搞？</blockquote><br />\n我之前都是上淘寶揾，之後用qq send 相比旅行社搞簽證，我是雙飛去，到出發果日，機場比Visa紙我"},{"pid":"f7384bd311338275406df8ec52b61a8e92fa54d0","tid":445581,"uid":90473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:22:49.000Z","msg":"搵丹東國旅都可以<br />\n算係全丹東最大規模嗰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b446db89adf62a64e4d07a68cc2cf74175162ad7","tid":445581,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵丹東國旅都可以<br />\n算係全丹東最大規模嗰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1283aea209e1c11ad706d49fa2adaa1a2bd3bc9","tid":445581,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislik